<HEADLINE>
<P>
KARABAKH CONFLICT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "David and Goliath in Caucasus" (April 21) presented a poignant view of the 
6-year-old conflict which has ravaged Nagorno-Karabakh and its Armenian 
population. Although the conviction and belief of Armenian freedom fighters in 
their just cause are indisputable, given the demographic imbalance of a handful 
of Armenians fighting millions of Azeris, the situation on the battleground 
will eventually reverse itself in favor of Azerbaijan. It is imperative that 
the international community undertake a lasting settlement in the region to 
avoid another Bosnian quagmire. 
</P>
<P>
 LORIG TITIZIAN 
</P>
<P>
