<P>
SWIMMER CORNUE SELECTS HARVARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Matt Cornue, a swimmer for Villa Park High, will attend Harvard, according to 
David Salo, who coaches the Irvine Novaquatics, Cornue's club. 
</P>
<P>
 Cornue won the 1993 Southern Section Division I title in the 100 freestyle. 
Harvard, which doesn't offer athletic scholarships, won the 1994 Ivy League 
men's swimming title. 
</P>
