<DATE>
<P>
May 2, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 2; Column 6; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
25 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pregnancy dreams -- The name of Frans Baert, a dream scholar and lecturer at 
Loyola Marymount University, was misspelled in April 27's Life & Style. 
</P>
</TEXT>
